      "cookedHtml": "<p>When in dashboard view, I combined multiple boards with subitems. I have spent plenty of time sizing the width of the columns for each board to be uniform.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>a column and row width adjustment feature like Excel would be amazing</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Even though i spent time making sure the columns are all visible on my screen at a time, not scrolling to the right to view all in the dashboard the screen skips to the right cutting off information to view blank space<br />\n2. scree fit options, remove the small scroll bar across the bottom unless needed<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/f/f9baad35a734c5ec69ab4b4a2057e7831bd3ab5c.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/f/f9baad35a734c5ec69ab4b4a2057e7831bd3ab5c_2_690x281.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"281\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1734×708 126 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/1/1ab5f24b7ab157bd3ed41b1751b7c1cfa4a0b676.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/1/1ab5f24b7ab157bd3ed41b1751b7c1cfa4a0b676_2_690x276.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"276\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1782×715 108 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/c/ce1093c5b435f123b35178f831eabf177ed41e2f.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/c/ce1093c5b435f123b35178f831eabf177ed41e2f_2_690x103.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"103\" />